  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6994 sitting right at the massive 7000 gamma wall (17.6B), dealers are actively selling into strength as their long gamma position forces them to fade the move higher. The PIN regime and towering positive gamma structure from 7000-7100 creates a strong ceiling effect, while the flip at 6876 provides downside support through dealer buying pressure. Watch for rejection at 7000 and potential mean reversion back toward 6950-6925, with 7025 as the next major resistance if 7000 breaks.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect the market to get pinned around 7000 with limited upside breakout potential.",
